name: Freaky Maze
description:
Freaky Maze is not any regular kind of maze game.You have to go through from challenging maze where maze changes and you have to find way to pass it. Game includes more than 150 level which are with twist when maze changes.You have to be calm,patience and smart to complete the level.

Controls:

Right side finishes level.

W/up arrow  player move up.

S/down arrow player move down.

A/left arrow player move left.

D/ right arrow  player move right.
